.TH TRUSTGET 1 "February 2026" "TrustGet 0.1.0" "User Commands"

.SH NAME
trustget, sg \- secure file downloader with automatic verification

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sg
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fIURL\fR
.br
.B trustget
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fIURL\fR

.SH DESCRIPTION
TrustGet is a secure alternative to wget that adds automatic verification and trust analysis.
It automatically finds and verifies checksums, analyzes GitHub Releases, and provides a
transparent trust score.

.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B sg download \fIURL\fR
Download file with automatic verification and trust analysis
.TP
.B sg verify \fIFILE\fR
Verify file against checksum
.TP
.B sg trust \fIURL\fR
Analyze trust score of URL without downloading
.TP
.B sg run \fIFILE\fR
Execute file with sandbox isolation
.TP
.B sg info \fIURL\fR
Show metadata about file/release without downloading
.TP
.B sg config
Manage TrustGet configuration

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-j ", " \-\-json
Output in JSON format
.TP
.BR \-q ", " \-\-quiet
Suppress non-essential output
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-verbose
Enable verbose output
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output
Output directory for downloaded file
.TP
.BR \-t ", " \-\-timeout
HTTP request timeout in seconds (default: 30)
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-retry
Number of retry attempts (default: 3)
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-force
Force download even if trust score is low
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-verify
Skip checksum verification
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-color
Disable colored output

.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Download with automatic verification:
.RS
.nf
$ sg https://github.com/cli/cli/releases/download/v2.40.0/gh_2.40.0_linux_amd64.tar.gz
.fi
.RE

.PP
Check trust score without downloading:
.RS
.nf
$ sg trust https://example.com/file.tar.gz
.fi
.RE

.PP
Verify local file:
.RS
.nf
$ sg verify ./file.tar.gz
.fi
.RE

.PP
JSON output for CI/CD:
.RS
.nf
$ sg \-\-json https://example.com/file.tar.gz | jq
.fi
.RE

.SH TRUST SCORE
TrustGet calculates a trust score (0-100) based on:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
HTTPS connection (+20)
.IP \(bu 2
Checksum verified (+25)
.IP \(bu 2
Known domain (+10)
.IP \(bu 2
Maintainer verified (+20)
.IP \(bu 2
Repository age > 1 year (+7)
.IP \(bu 2
Recent release (+10)
.IP \(bu 2
Unknown domain (\-20)
.IP \(bu 2
No checksum (\-15)
.RE

.Risk Levels:
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
CRITICAL (<40): Abort download
.IP \(bu 2
HIGH (40-59): Confirm with user
.IP \(bu 2
MEDIUM (60-79): Proceed with warning
.IP \(bu 2
LOW (80-100): Safe to proceed
.RE

.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B TRUSTGET_GITHUB_TOKEN
GitHub personal access token for higher API rate limits

.SH FILES
.TP
.B ~/.config/trustget/config.toml
Configuration file

.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success
.TP
.B 1
General error or download failed
.TP
.B 2
Checksum verification failed

